author: Seet Matthew
text:
Been here a couple of times as my nearest AF is closed for renovations.

To be fair to AFGB, everything within the gym so far has been great! There are some machines that were missing from my expectations but that is not a big issue nor the reason why I gave 4 stars.

I usually workout at AFGB in the early mornings before dawn. I gave 4 stars as AFGB is located inside Kolam Ayer CC, which means that all toilets are locked up until 10am (as written on a sign outside the toilet by the CC).If you need a toilet for nature calls (or a shower after gym to go to work, not sure if there are showers in there)... You're screwed.

I hope AFGB can work something out with the CC, perhaps having a key for the toilets kept inside the gym that members can use for emergency needs.

**EDIT: I went again today and noticed there was indeed a key for the toilets. Changing my 4 star review to a 5 star. Sorry!
